{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Line a large baking tray (30 x 40 cm) with paper cupcake liners of various sizes (approx. 30-40) (see Tips). Set aside.","Place chocolate into mixing bowl and melt <b>3 min\/90°C\/speed 3<b>.","Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula and melt <b>4 min\/90°C\/speed 3<b>.","Transfer ½ teaspoon or 1 teaspoon of melted chocolate into each liner (½ teaspoon for mini cupcake liners, 1 teaspoon for standard size liners). Use a straw or skewer to spread chocolate in a circular motion to the edges to cover base of liner (see Tips).","Place a bowl onto mixing bowl lid and weigh sprinkles into it. Working quickly, scatter 1-2 teaspoons of sprinkles over chocolate (1 teaspoon for mini cupcake liners, 2 teaspoons for standard ones) so chocolate is completely covered. Allow chocolate to set slightly (approx. 1 minute), then quickly tip excess sprinkles back into bowl.","Transfer into freezer for a minimum of 30 minutes to set. Unwrap freckles and store in a freezable container until ready to use."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["300 g dairy free white chocolate, broken into pieces","100 - 200 g gluten free 100s and 1000s sprinkles"]}],"id":"r119432","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-NHCIQEZkf4M\/XZWe3LQ9ZhI\/AAAAAAAAe64\/S6_htim7S24z0YQ7Lau5sAAG5Ftf_X4FACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_jCqcTQjQmBDQSg3V.png","title":"Freckles","publishedAt":"2017-10-16T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"0.3 g","fat":"3.1 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"12.6 g","calories":"327 kJ \/ 77 kcal"},"usefulItems":"cupcake liners, baking tray (30 x 40 cm), cupcake liners, wooden skewer, bowl, freezable storage container, freezer","hintsAndTricks":["This recipe will make 30-40 freckles depending on the size of the cupcake liners or moulds used.","To make larger freckles, use Texas muffin liners or large silicone muffin moulds.","If the chocolate hardens, mix <strong data-mce-contenteditable=\"false\">3 min\/50°C\/speed 2<\/strong>, or until chocolate melts again.","You can use a combination of milk, white and dark chocolate.","You can make the freckles as far in advance as you like. Store them in a container in the freezer until ready to use."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h","30 pieces"]}